{"word":"Tabernacle","slug":"tabernacle","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tabernacle</b> One existed before Moses received the pattern authorized on Mount Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=11'>Exo 33:11</a><br/> The one instituted by Moses was called:<br/> - Sanctuary<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=8'>Exo 25:8</a> <br/> - Tabernacle (or Tent) of Meeting<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a> <br/> - Tabernacle (or Tent)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=7'>Exo 33:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=5'>2Ch 5:5</a> <br/> - Tabernacle (or Tent) of Testimony<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=21'>Exo 38:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=50'>Num 1:50</a> <br/> - Tent of Testimony<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=8'>Num 17:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=6'>2Ch 24:6</a> <br/> - Temple of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=9'>1Sa 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Sa 3:3</a> <br/> - House of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=24'>Jos 6:24</a> <br/> Pattern of, revealed to Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=9'>Exo 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=30'>Exo 26:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=32'>Exo 39:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=43'>Exo 39:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=44'>Act 7:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=8&vers